<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="poemXX">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>vaḷarat toṭiṉum vauvupu tirintu</l>
<l>viḷari yuṟutarun tīntoṭai niṉaiyāt</l>
<l>taḷaru neñcan talaii maṉaiyō</l>
<l>ḷuḷaruṅ kūnta ṉōkkik kaḷara</l>
<l>kaḷḷi nīḻaṟ kaṭavuḷ vāḻttip</l>
<l>pacipaṭu maruṅkulai kacipukai toḻāak</l>
<l>kāṇaleṉ kolleṉa viṉaviṉai varūum</l>
<l>pāṇa kēṇmati yāṇaratu nilaiyē</l>
<l>puravuttoṭut tuṇkuvai yāyiṉu miravuyeḻun</l>
<l>tevvaṅ koḷkuvai yāyiṉu miraṇṭuṅ</l>
<l>kaiyuḷa pōluṅ kaṭitaṇ maiyavē</l>
<l>muṉṉūrp pūcaliṟ ṟōṉṟit taṉṉūr</l>
<l>neṭunirai taḻīiya mīḷi yāḷar</l>
<l>viṭukaṇai nīttan tuṭipuṇai yāka</l>
<l>veṉṟi tantu koṉṟukōḷ viṭuttu</l>
<l>vaiyakam pulampa vaḷaiiya pāmpiṉ</l>
<l>vaiyeyiṟ ṟuynta matiyiṉ maṟavar</l>
<l>kaiyakat tuynta kaṉṟuṭaip pallā</l>
<l>ṉiraiyoṭu vanta vuraiya ṉāki</l>
<l>yurikaḷai yarava māṉat tāṉē</l>
<l>yarituce lulakiṟ ceṉṟaṉa ṉuṭampē</l>
<l>kāṉac ciṟṟiyāṟ ṟaruṅkaraik kāluṟṟuk</l>
<l>kampamoṭu tuḷaṅkiya vilakkam pōla</l>
<l>vampoṭu tuḷaṅki yāṇṭoḻin taṉṟē</l>
<l>yuyaricai veṟuppat tōṉṟiya peyarē</l>
<l>maṭañcāṉ maññai yaṇimayir cūṭṭi</l>
<l>yiṭampiṟar koḷḷāc ciṟuvaḻip</l>
<l>paṭañcey pantark kaṉmicai yatuvē.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
